OL,3,CCaller told 999 operator he'd murder
OL,4,Cher amid rise in abuse for emergency
OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,FA Welsh Ambulance Service worker has
OL,8,Fdescribed how a caller verbally abused
OL,9,Fher by telling her he would "cut her
OL,10,Finto pieces" and murder her.
OL,12,FAbbie Williams is a WAS call
OL,13,Fsupervisor in Cwmbran and says she has
OL,14,Fexperienced several incidents of
OL,15,Fverbal abuse while trying to help
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,FIt is a problem that many other
OL,19,Femergency workers have to deal with,
OL,20,Ftoo.
