OL,3,CCaller told 999 operator he'd murder
OL,4,Cher amid rise in abuse for emergency
OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,FNew data has show that there were
OL,8,F1,964 incidents of verbal abuse
OL,9,Fagainst Welsh emergency workers
OL,10,Fbetween April 2019 and December 2023.
OL,12,FMore than a third (37%) of the victims
OL,13,Fwere police workers, while more than
OL,14,Fhalf (52%) were medical workers.
OL,16,FAbbie said: "The first abusive call I
OL,17,Fremember was in Covid-19 when the
OL,18,Fcaller said he'd cut me up into
OL,19,Fpieces, even going into detail about
OL,20,Fwhich body part he'd start with and
OL,21,Fwhat tools he'd use to do it.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/15
