OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,F"He described in graphic detail how
OL,8,Fhe'd murder me ` that one will always
OL,9,Fstay with me.
OL,11,F"Other callers have said they hope I
OL,12,Fcrash my car on the way home, or that
OL,13,FI never get to see my family again.
OL,15,F"I do understand that emotions are
OL,16,Fheightened when you or your loved one
OL,17,Fis ill, but we're trying our best to
OL,18,Fhelp you.
