OL,7,F"Sometimes the calls are in quick
OL,8,Fsuccession so you're going from one
OL,9,Fabusive call to another, or worse, a
OL,10,Ftraumatic call when someone has died.
OL,12,F"Those have a cumulative effect and
OL,13,Fyou get more upset and triggered.
OL,15,F"I don't think people realise how much
OL,16,Fit impacts our mental health.
OL,18,F"Their words could be going around in
OL,19,Fyour head for weeks.
