OL,7,F"You do become more resilient with
OL,8,Fexperience, but we're losing a lot of
OL,9,Fgood call takers because of this.
OL,11,F"We're doing this job because we want
OL,12,Fto help people, and we're all trying
OL,13,Four best.
OL,15,F"Please be kind."
OL,17,FEmma Worrall, a 999 call taker in
OL,18,FLlangunnor, Carmarthenshire, recalls
OL,19,Fhow one man threatened to stab her.
