OL,7,FShe said: "When I started this role
OL,8,Ffour years ago, verbal abuse was rare,
OL,9,Fbut now it's a daily occurrence,
OL,10,Fespecially if there are long waits for
OL,11,Fan ambulance.
OL,13,F"It's to the point now where we
OL,14,Factually celebrate those callers who
OL,15,Fare pleasant and thank us for the
OL,16,Fgreat work we do.
OL,18,F"When you tell someone it might be 6-8
OL,19,Fhours for an ambulance, it's like the
OL,20,Fflick of a switch.
