OL,7,FJason Killens, chief executive of the
OL,8,FWelsh Ambulance Service, said:
OL,9,F"Stories of physical abuse towards
OL,10,Ffrontline ambulance crews are all too
OL,11,Ffamiliar, but control room staff also
OL,12,Freceive horrid verbal abuse on a daily
OL,13,Fbasis.
OL,15,F"Call takers are the first person you
OL,16,Finteract with when you call 999 for an
OL,17,Fambulance.
