OL,7,F"If you ever need to call 999 or 111,
OL,8,Fplease be courteous and treat our
OL,9,Fpeople with respect."
OL,11,FIn 2021, emergency services in Wales
OL,12,Flaunched their With Us, Not Against Us
OL,13,Fcampaign in a bid to reduce assaults.
OL,15,FPam Kelly, chief constable of Gwent
OL,16,FPolice, said: "Nobody should expect to
OL,17,Fbe assaulted ` either physically or
OL,18,Fverbally ` when they go to work,
OL,19,Fwhether you work for the emergency
OL,20,Fservices or otherwise.
