OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,F"It saddens me to hear of these
OL,8,Fterrible encounters that my staff and
OL,9,Fthose across the emergency services
OL,10,Fhave experienced when they were
OL,11,Fassaulted by the public in the line of
OL,12,Fduty.
OL,14,F"This behaviour makes our roles more
OL,15,Fchallenging, and we will support any
OL,16,Fofficer or emergency service worker
OL,17,Fwho has experienced this disgraceful
OL,18,Fabuse while also taking firm actions
OL,19,Fagainst those responsible."
