OL,8,Fsentence under the Assault on
OL,9,FEmergency Workers (Offences) Act which
OL,10,Fcould be applied by the magistrates'
OL,11,Fcourt was doubled from six months to
OL,12,F12 months in prison.
OL,14,FIn 2022, the maximum custodial
OL,15,Fsentence which could be applied by a
OL,16,Fcrown court was increased to two years.
